Create a list from an R6 object

Source: R/aslist.R
as.list.R6.Rd

This returns a list of public members from the object. It simply calls as.list.environment.

# S3 method for R6
as.list(x, ...)

Arguments

x

An R6 object.

...

Other arguments, which will be ignored.
